==Description== <!--T:3-->

<!--T:14-->
'''Part MakeFace'''‏‎ creates a planar face from a given set of coplanar closed wires. The wires can be any valid wire, i.e. created in [[Part_Workbench|Part WB]], [[Draft_Workbench|Draft WB]] or a [[Sketcher_Workbench|sketch]].

<!--T:15-->
It is possible to nest closed (non-intersecting) contours, for example having circles inside a polygon, or simply two different wires, as shown in the picture below.

